## Basic Information
The SEGUE targeting information for
all fibers associated with a given plate.  The format is the same as
the <a href="/datamodel/files/SSPP_REDUX/targets/all/segueTarget.html"> full
target files</a> .

### Naming Convention
segueTargetPlate-PLATE4-MJD.fits

### Releases
DR8

### Enviroments
SSPP_REDUX

### Approximate Size
357 KB

### File Type
FITS

### Generated by Product
sas

### HDU List for release DR8
  - [HDU0: PRIMARY](#hdu0-primary)
  - [HDU1: ](#hdu1-)

### HDU0: PRIMARY


#### HDU Type: IMAGE
#### HDU Size:  0 bytes

##### Header Table Caption for HDU0
Key | Value | Comment | |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| SIMPLE | True | conforms to FITS standard |
| BITPIX | 8 | array data type |
| NAXIS | 0 | number of array dimensions |
| EXTEND | True |  |
